'''Asenğaq amaziγ''' yettwanulfa-d eg iseggasen n 70 sγur [[agraw imaziγen]] (l'Académie berbère). Deg 1998, s ifassen n u-Congrès mondial amazigh (CMA)  iy gan agraw-nsen amenzu deg tigzirin tikanariyen eg Tmurt n Spanya, asenğaq-agi yuγal d asenğaq amens'ub n imaziγen akken ma ttilin ukk ttidiren deg umad'al marra.

Γur-es krad (3) n yiniten (colors) : [[az'erwal]], [[azegzaw]], [[awraγ]]. Geg tlemmas-is yettwars [[asekkil|usekkil]] s yini (color) azegwaγ (aza neγ yez) s [[tifinaγ]] .

*Az'erwal anamek-is d (ill)agrakal (mediteranien sea). 
*Azegzaw anamek-is tagama (nature) n [[tefriqt ugafa]]. 
*Awraγ anamek-is d tiniri n tefriqt ugafa (desert neγ Sahara).

